在[[電機工程學|電機工程學]]領域裡，shmoo圖是一個圖形化顯示，反應一個條件範圍或輸入的系統元件變化。

==源起==
shmoo圖的起源，是不清楚的。它是參考1966年的[[电气电子工程师学会|电气电子工程师学会]]的論文。<ref>[https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/5217603/ The Sensitivity Function in Variability Analysis] {{Wayback|url=https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/5217603/ |date=20180610050625 }}, Charles Belove, [[IEEE|IEEE]] Transactions on Reliability, Volume R-15, Issue 2, August 1966.</ref> 其它早期的參考是來自{{le|IBM 2365處理器儲存元件|IBM 2365 Processor Storage}}的手冊。<ref>[https://www.staff.ncl.ac.uk/roger.broughton/museum/corestore/ram64k.htm 64KByte gate in a Core Storage Unit] {{Wayback|url=https://www.staff.ncl.ac.uk/roger.broughton/museum/corestore/ram64k.htm |date=20170215194946 }}, Virtual Museum, [[Newcastle_University|Newcastle University]]. According to the [https://www.staff.ncl.ac.uk/roger.broughton/museum/index.htm Virtual Museum] {{Wayback|url=https://www.staff.ncl.ac.uk/roger.broughton/museum/index.htm |date=20170402191625 }} page, this computer was installed in 1967.</ref>

shmoo圖的發明，有些人把功勞歸於VLSI名人堂的[[羅伯特．休斯頓|羅伯特．休斯頓]](Robert Huston, 1941-2006)。<ref>[https://www.chiphistory.org/TCI%20All_Stars-Hall_of_Fame%20161212.pdf VLSIresearch’s CHIP MAKING INDUSTRY HALL OF FAME] {{Wayback|url=https://www.chiphistory.org/TCI%20All_Stars-Hall_of_Fame%20161212.pdf |date=20170102234827 }}, VLSI Research Inc.</ref>因為休斯頓在1967年前並未擔任測試工程師，這可能不是真的。<ref>[http://www.legacy.com/obituaries/mercurynews/obituary.aspx?n=robert-e-huston&pid=18711143 Robert Huston Obituary] {{Wayback|url=http://www.legacy.com/obituaries/mercurynews/obituary.aspx?n=robert-e-huston&pid=18711143 |date=20201107081232 }}, [[San_Jose_Mercury_News|San Jose Mercury News]], July 31 2006</ref>

